videos.description: Dru Brown completes a pass to Braydon Johnson, who takes it all the way to the house for a 42-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma State strikes 1st on Johnson’s 42-yard TD) 2019/12/27

videos.headline: Oklahoma State strikes 1st on Johnson's 42-yard TD

videos.description: Dru Brown fakes the handoff and keeps it himself, jumping over a defender to put Oklahoma State up 14-0.
